"title": "7480: wave offering",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7480: wave offering",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A gift specially dedicated to God. The term itself may not be intended to convey a particular action.</p>\n<h2>The wave offering was part of every fellowship offering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:34\">LEV 7:34</a></strong> <em>Although given to the priests, the offering belonged to the LORD.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:28-Lev7:32\">LEV 7:28–7:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:21\">LEV 9:21</a></p>\n<h2>The wave offering was eaten by the priests</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:26-Exod29:28\">EXO 29:26–29:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:15\">LEV 10:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:11\">NUM 18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:18\">NUM 18:18</a></p>\n<h2>Occasions for making a wave offering</h2>\n<h3>As a cereal offering when priests were consecrated</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:23-Exod29:24\">EXO 29:23–29:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:27-Lev8:29\">LEV 8:27–8:29</a></p>\n<h3>As a guilt offering sacrificed at a ceremonial cleansing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:12\">LEV 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:21\">LEV 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:24\">LEV 14:24</a></p>\n<h3>As part of the ritual when a woman was accused of adultery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:25\">NUM 5:25</a></p>\n<h3>When celebrating harvest</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:10-Lev23:11\">LEV 23:10–23:11</a> <em>the firstfruits of the harvest</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:15-Lev23:17\">LEV 23:15–23:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:20\">LEV 23:20</a></p>\n<h3>When presenting a gift to God</h3>\n<p>Materials given for constructing the tabernacle:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:24\">EXO 38:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:29\">EXO 38:29</a></p>\n<h3>When dedicating the Levites to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:11\">NUM 8:11</a></strong> <em>The dedication to God of the Levites symbolised the consecration of the whole nation.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:13\">NUM 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:15\">NUM 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:21\">NUM 8:21</a></p>",
